    <p>
      <em>Questions to Consider:</em>
    </p>
    <p>
      <ul xml:id="m00049-list-00003">
        <li>
          <p>What is the process for applying to college?</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <p>What do I need to consider when making a decision about what college to attend?</p>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </p>
    <p>In the previous sections in this chapter, you learned about the types of colleges and universities and what to consider as you begin researching where you would like to go. This section focuses on the steps for applying to college and what you can do to prepare to make an informed decision. No matter how many months or years you have before you enroll in a college or university, you can start now to get organized and prepare.</p>
